Needs the following python libraries:
subprocess
optparse
re

Install libraries using:
"pip install library_name"

Arguments:
-h, --help: display information about the arhuments
-i, --interface: specify the interface whose MAC address is to be changed
-m, --mac: specify the new MAC address to change into

Usage:
cd into the folder containing mac_changer.py
"python mac_changer -i interface_name -m 11:22:33:44:55:66" # changes mac address of "interface_name" to 11:22:33:44:55:66
